# No Sparkles Icon

**Do not use the `Sparkles` icon from lucide-react.** The user finds it generic and prefers context-specific icons.

## Replacements by Context

| Context | Use Instead |
|---------|-------------|
| Published/approved content | `CheckCircle2` |
| Explore/discover | `Compass` |
| Writing/author/create | `PenLine` |
| Latest/recent posts | `Clock` |
| Activity feed | `Activity` |
| Empty states (posts, drafts) | `FileText` or `BookOpen` |
| Activate/complete | `Check` |
